    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. Six factors appropriately scoped out at MRL 2. Validation evidence from the FDA generic centrifugal pump demonstrates RH predictions within 8% of experimental values. The CFD model is deemed credible for identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions under CPB use. Note: supporting evidence documents referenced in the validation literature confirm model adequacy, though formal provenance linkage from the primary claim to individual evidence nodes was not established in this submission package.",
